	(text "24V -> 5V\n\nVmax = 12 * 10/(47+10) + 2.5 = 4.6V\nG = 1+(100k/Rg)\nGain = G * 10/(47+10) = 0.175\n\nfc = 1 / ( 2pi * 47kx10k * 1n ) = 19kHz\n\n-Imax@2V5 = (12+2.5)/100x(47k+10k) = 400 uA\n+Imax@2V5 = (12-2.5)/100x(47k+10k) = 260 uA"
